    <version>0.7.0</version>
    <time>1773258698</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>sso-mib provides a library and command line utilities that talk to the himmelblau identity broker. They can be used to provide integration for software that requires asking for a PRT SSO cookie for Entra, which is needed when the Entra tenant enables Conditional Access.

One of the provided tools, for example, is a git credentials manager that allows one to use git send-email with an O365 email address that requires Conditional Access tokens for auth.

https://github.com/siemens/sso-mib

Requires libjwt as a build dependency which will also be sent.</comment>
    <requestid>1338008</requestid>
  </revision>
  <revision rev="2" vrev="1">
